version_description:
- Play Quick Mode
- Send gifts to opponents while playing the game.
- Join or Create a club with players around the world !!
- UX improvement
- Lots of under the hood improvement to make game bug freeKill Token Boost (Use the boost to open kill chest at 3x faster speed)

Exciting new update ------
That you have been waiting for!
BET IN "PLAY WITH FRIENDS"

Introducing 
Big Win : Play 5M Bets for an hour each day. 10M/25M on weekends.
Clubs get got better :
- Club Leagues : Collect Club points & climb up the Club Leagues every week
- Open & close Clubs gets changed into Public & private.  Club leader can choose who to allow/not in Private clubs
A Complete makeover of the game. Tons of graphic/UI improvements

Introducing
- Snake & Ladders Game : Relax, Roll the dice & Relive your Childhood
- Biggest Sale of season : Special Ramadan Offer with an exclusive Dice
- Play with friends without Bet : Now you can play with friends without bet as well
- A lot of under the hood fixes to make your experience better
